            <div type="transcript" id="J605">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Spider holds a Silver Ball</l>
                    <l>In unperceived Hands --</l>
                    <l>And dancing softly to Himself</l>
                    <l><app type="revision"><lem>Pursues his pearly strands --</lem><rdg>Pursues his pearly strands --</rdg></app>
His Yarn of Pearl -- unwinds --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>He plies from Nought to Nought --</l>
                    <l>In unsubstantial Trade --</l>
                    <l>Supplants our Tapestries with His --</l>
                    <l>In half the period --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>An Hour to rear supreme</l>
                    <l>His <app type="revision"><lem>Theories</lem><rdg>Theories</rdg></app>
Continents of Light --</l>
                    <l>Then <app type="revision"><lem>perish by</lem><rdg>perish by</rdg></app>
dangle from the Housewife's Broom --</l>
                    <l>His <app type="revision"><lem>Sophistries --</lem><rdg>Sophistries --</rdg></app>
Boundaries -- forgot --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>3.to Himself] as He knits</l>
                    <l>4.Yarn] Coil --</l>
                    <l>4.unwinds] expends --</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
